The '''[[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] Missile Trooper''', or "Anti-Air Troopers", were infantry units used for destroying airborne vessels by the [[Gungan Grand Army/Legends|Gungan Grand Army]]. The units were not as resilient as [[Raaptur]]s or Gungan Fighters, but offered ground units some protection against air attacks.

